{"tid":1640121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身邊有淺黃中年人 唔明白神獸意義","createTime":"2019-10-09T00:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T01:46:54.000Z","uid":207713,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e0cfe36c7cc087d6d234472b2e7782b0447fac","tid":1640121,"uid":207713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:38:38.000Z","msg":"小妹從事教育行業，其實間學校都算係咁，學生有言論自由，老師都知道黑警真係好過份，唔係會盲撐黑警同政府既無腦袋生物。<br />\n<br />\n但今日番到教員室時，聽到佢地討論神獸問題，「就算政見唔同，都唔洗打到人咁樣呀？」係佢地講得最多既一句，我覺得佢地係唔知道出動神獸既前提係佢主動向抗爭者施襲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔通你走黎屌我一句就郁手咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想佢地再誤會前線，可以點樣令佢地明白？<br />\n<br />\n我係學校只係一個新入職既小小老師，亦好鍾意呢間學校，唔想一黎就講太多野令佢地篤我背脊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我淨係諗到印下文宣痴係學校，等佢地行過希望會望到"},{"pid":"61b74c1bce8995112263873ba8d864c14585d95c","tid":1640121,"uid":207713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:41:09.000Z","msg":"推1/5"},{"pid":"7eaaedd83a233e1a1fd43d12da40e3b5d21dadf7","tid":1640121,"uid":207713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:47:39.000Z","msg":"推2/5"},{"pid":"0dbb4180107dd746a602bafa6d76dcfc78237a99","tid":1640121,"uid":272485,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ww09jpZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fww09jpZ.jpg&h=a8152c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kj86541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKj86541.jpg&h=09098e58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZA5CbJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZA5CbJ.jpg&h=3cf871ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YGfM546.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYGfM546.jpg&h=780b08ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0XXWJRN.jpg\"